E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20name-calling%20backfired%20and%20impacted%20how%20the%20respondents%20viewed%20the%20perpetrating%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20effect%20we%20found%20was%20all%20focused%20on%20the%20actual%20attacker%2C%26quot%3B%20Dusso%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDusso's%20study%20also%20found%20some%20partisan%20differences%20in%20the%20impact%20of%20name-calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20Democratic%20candidate%20uses%20a%20pejorative%20or%20engages%20in%20name-calling%2C%20Republican%20and%20Democratic%20respondents%20rated%20the%20candidate%20lower.%20However%2C%20when%20a%20Republican%20candidate%20engaged%20in%20the%20same%20tactic%2C%20the%20respondents'%20perceptions%20did%20not%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20just%20kind%20of%20shrug%20their%20shoulders%2C%26quot%3B%20Dusso%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20study%20explains%20what%20explains%20the%20%26quot%3Bpartisan%20symmetry%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20there%20is%20some%20speculation.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BThe%20obvious%20is%20that%20this%20is%20happening%20so%20much%20on%20the%20right%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20left%20that%20we%20become%20numb%20to%20it%20happening%20on%20the%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Dusso%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20don't%20really%20notice%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-nikki-haley-racist-name-calling-threat-nimbra-election-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705883340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65adb5b7617029e90a5edddd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-nikki-haley-racist-name-calling-threat-nimbra-election-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20called%20Nikki%20Haley%20a%20racist%20name%20on%20Friday%2C%20par%20for%20the%20course%20for%20someone%20who%20turns%20to%20name-ca