mg%20width%3D%5C%221980%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kathleen%20Murray%20smiles%20on%20her%20lawn%2C%20which%20won%20her%20a%20contest%20because%20it's%20so%20dry%20and%20ugly.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ad8a87dcdb354a98597cc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221418%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKathleen%20Murray%20smiles%20on%20her%20lawn%2C%20which%20won%20her%20a%20contest%20due%20to%20its%20ugliness%20and%20dryness.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gotland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20Australian%20woman%20won%20a%20Swedish%20competition%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BWorld's%20Ugliest%20Lawn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20competition%20was%20launched%20to%20promote%20global%20water%20conservation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKathleen%20Murray%20said%20she%20relies%20on%C2%A0%26quot%3Bnature's%20lawn%20mowers%2C%26quot%3B%20like%C2%A0wallabies%2C%20kangaroos%2C%20and%20echidnas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20would%20consider%20it%20a%20compliment%2C%20but%20an%20Australian%20woman%20is%20thrilled%20after%20an%20international%20panel%20gave%20her%20the%20%26quot%3BWorld's%20Ugliest%20Lawn%26quot%3B%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20from%20the%20Swedish%20island%20of%20Gotland%20launched%20the%20competition%20to%20%26quot%3Bsave%20water%20by%20changing%20the%20norm%20of%20green%20lawns%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgotland.com%2Fworlds-ugliest-lawn%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20island.%20Judges%20included%20Gotland%20officials%20and%20individuals%20from%20Ireland%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20genius%20of%20this%20competition.%20It%20uses%20humor%20to%20shine%20a%20light%20on%20such%20a%20serious%20subject%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20awards%20those%20willing%20to%20proudly%20proclaim%20that%20theirs%20is%20the%20lawn%20which%20deserves%20disgusted%20glances%20from%20neighbors%20%E2%80%93%20and%20a%20round%20of%20applause%20from%20around%20the%20globe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20prize%2C%20the%20Swedish%20competition%20awarded%20Kathleen%20Murray%20of%20Tasmania%20with%20a%20%26quot%3BProud%20owner%20of%20The%20World's%20Ugliest%20Lawn%26quot%3B%20t-shirt.%20The%20press%20release%20noted%20that%20all%20contestants%20had%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20ugliness%20to%20be%20proud%20of%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20dry%20yards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKathleen%20Murray's%20lawn%20boasts%20deep%2C%20dry%20divots%20created%20by%20three%20wild%20bandicoots%20(small%20marsupials%20endemic%20to%20Australia)%20and%20not%20one%20dust-covered%20decimeter%20is%20wasted%20on%20watering.%20For%20that%2C%20the%20planet%2C%20and%20its%20dwindling%20stockpiles%20of%20life-giving%20liquid%2C%20thanks%20you%2C%C2%A0Kathleen%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurray%2C%20a%2053-year-old%20mother%20of%20four%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fclimate-environment%2F2024%2F01%2F19%2Ftasmania-worlds-ugliest-lawn%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20meant%20to%20start%20landscaping%20her%20yard%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20she%20just%20gave%20up%2C%20allowing%20local%20burrowers%20and%20grazers%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20wallabies%2C%20kangaroos%2C%20echidnas%2C%20and%20bandicoots%20%E2%80%94%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bnature's%20lawn%20mowers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20think%20my%20backyard%20is%20ugly%2C%26quot%3B%20Murray%20told%20the%20Post.%20%26quot%3BThey%20think%20it's%20beautiful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-ugliest-lawn-winner-says-animals-think-its-beautiful-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705875466000%2C%