tions%20for%20chickens%2C%20turkeys%2C%20and%20pigs%2C%20but%20is%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bunacceptable%26quot%3B%20for%20other%20mammals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20a%20federal%20appeals%20court%20heard%20arguments%20from%20Smith's%20attorney%20in%20a%20last-minute%20effort%20to%20block%20the%20execution%2C%20saying%20a%20second%20execution%20attempt%20would%20constitute%20cruel%20and%20unusual%20punishment.%20Alabama's%20solicitor%20general%20argued%20that%20the%20state%20has%20%26quot%3Badopted%20the%20most%20painless%20and%20humane%20method%20of%20execution%20known%20to%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Falabama-execution-nitrogen-gas-hypoxia-f8b818b74542783612a0574de65cc0c2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nitrogen%20hypoxia%20execution%20method%2C%20which%20remains%20untested%2C%20involves%20a%20mask%20being%20fitted%20to%20the%20prisoner's%20face%2C%20which%20pipes%20in%20nitrogen%20gas.%20But%20Smith's%20lawyer%20has%20argued%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20that%20the%20mask's%20seal%20could%20leak%20in%20oxygen%2C%20causing%20a%20prolonged%20and%20terrifying%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20appeals%20judges%20on%20Friday%20also%20asked%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20Smith%20vomited%20into%20the%20mask%20%E2%80%94%20to%20which%20Alabama's%20solicitor%20general%20responded%20that%20the%20state%20would%20not%20stop%20the%20nitrogen%20gas%20once%20it%20began%20flowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20vomits%20during%20the%20execution%20with%20the%20mask%20on%2C%20you're%20telling%20me%20that%20the%20state%20will%20not%20stop%20the%20execution%2C%20they%20will%20permit%20him%20to%20choke%20on%20his%20vomit%3F%26quot%3B%20one%20judge%20asked%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press.%20The%20solicitor%20general%20replied%20that%20the%20risk%20of%20vomiting%20was%20low%20and%20that%20Smith%20would%20be%20unconscious%20almost%20immed