i%20has%20been%20in%20sensational%20form%20of%20late.%20He%20was%20the%20top-scorer%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20last%20year%20as%20India%20reached%20the%20final%2C%20only%20to%20go%20down%20against%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2011%20matches%2C%20Kohli%20amassed%20765%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2095.62.%20He%20also%20broke%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E's%20record%20of%20most%20ODI%20centuries%20with%20his%20knock%20in%20the%20semi-final%20against%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20scored%208%2C848%20runs%20in%20113%20Test%20matches%20for%20India%20at%20an%20average%20of%2049.15%2C%20while%20scoring%2030%20fifties%2C%2029%20hundreds%20and%20seven%20double%20hundreds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20squad%20for%20first%20two%20Tests%20vs%20England%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20(C)%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20(wk)%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KS%20Bharat%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs