film%2Fnews%2Fjesse-eisenberg-a-real-pain-sundance-searchlight-mega-deal-1235880914%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMeri%20Hi%20Billi...%26quot%3B%3A%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20Swipe%20At%20Himanta%20Sarma%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20alleged%20that%20BJP%20engineered%20yesterday's%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20said%20then%20Congress%20will%20not%20be%20intimidated%2C%20no%20matter%20what.%20In%20the%20passing%2C%20he%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20who%20once%20belonged%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam's%20ruling%20BJP%20is%20so%20%26quot%3Bscared%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20success%20of%20Congress's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20that%20they%20attacked%20the%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Bhupen%20Kumar%20Borah%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Nagaon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20last%20year's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20passed%20through%20several%20BJP-ruled%20states%2C%20%26quot%3Bno%20stone%20was%20hurled%26quot%3B%20at%20it%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20which%20has%20the%20RSS%20headquarters%2C%20lakhs%20of%20people%20joined%20us%20and%20there%20was%20no%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20it%20happening%20in%20Assam%3F%20It%20is%20happening%20here%20because%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra)%20Modi%20ji's%20'chela'%20(disciple)%2C%20who%20blindly%20listens%20to%20his%20'sahab'%20(boss)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20state%20Congress%20chief%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Mr%20Borah)%20is%20not%20afraid%2C%20nor%20any%20Congress%20worker...%20We%20have%20seen%20many%20such.%20This%20is%20like%20having%20my%20cat%20growl%20at%20me...%20We%20did%20not%20fear%20the%20British.%20No%20question%20of%20being%20afraid%20of%20the%20BJP%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20claimed%20BJP%20supporters%20attacked%20its%20Assam%20unit%20chief%20Bhupen%20Bora%20in%20Jamuguri%20haat%20under%20Sonitpur%20district%2C%20as%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20entered%20Assam%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20He%20and%20party%20worker%20Hridoy%20Das%20were%20injured%2C%20the%20party%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20also%20alleged%20that%20a%20group%20of%20BJP%20workers%20tried%20to%20attack%20party%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20case%20was%20filed%20today%20following%20a%20complaint%20by%20the%20Congress.%20The%20party%20declared%20that%20it%20has%20no%20faith%20on%20the%20police%20inquiry%20and%20demanded%20a%20judicial%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20he%20confronted%20a%20group%20of%20BJP%20workers%20who%20tried%20to%20block%20and%20interrupt%20the%20Yatra%20in%20Assam.%20As%20the%20BJP%20workers%20tried%20to%20stop%20the%20bus%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20got%20off%20and%20talked%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20public%20meeting%2C%20he%20later%20said%20the%20Congress%20workers%20can't%20be%20cowed%20down.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20not%20scared%20of%20your%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20or%20your%20local%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20posted%20a%20a%20video%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20getting%20off%20a%20car%20amid%20scuffle%20between%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20supporters.%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20eve%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Lalla's%20Pran%20Pratishtha%2C%20Ram%20Bhakts%20have%20every%20right%20to%20chant%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20shouldn't%20lose%20his%20cool%20and%20be%20allergic%20to%20the%20chanting%20of%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram.%20He%20cannot%20instigate%20violence%20and%20threaten%20the%20public%20in%20this%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20post%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20BJP%20also%20hit%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Speaker%20of%20Assam%20Assembly%20and%20B