2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107033492%2Cimgsize-104754.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fhema-malini-shares-her-experience-as-ayodhya-gears-up-for-pran-pratishtha-ceremony-of-ram-mandir-i-am-getting-goosebumps-seeing-everything%2Farticleshow%2F107033471.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107033471.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHema%20Malini%20has%20graced%20Ayodhya%20with%20her%20presence%20ahead%20of%20the%20highly%20anticipated%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20scheduled%20for%20January%2022.%20The%20veteran%20actress%2C%20who%20is%20already%20soaking%20in%20the%20vibrant%20energy%20of%20the%20preparations%2C%20took%20to%20Twitter%20to%20express%20her%20excitement%20and%20share%20her%20experiences%20as%20Ayodhya%20gears%20up%20for%20this%20historic%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fhema-malini-shares-her-experience-as-ayodhya-gears-up-for-pran-pratishtha-ceremony-of-ram-mandir-i-am-getting-goosebumps-seeing-everything%2Farticleshow%2F107033471.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nightmarish%20Resurgence%20Of%20Rats%20In%20Ukraine%20Echoes%20WWI%20Horrors%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20war-ridden%20frontlines%20of%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20are%20grappling%20with%20a%20nightmarish%20resurgence%20of%20rats%20and%20mice%2C%20echoing%20the%20haunting%20conditions%20of%20World%20War%20I%20trench%20warfare%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20infestation%2C%20fuelled%20by%20a%20static%20war%20situation%20and%20harsh%20winter%20conditions%2C%20is%20not%20only%20spreading%20disease%20among%20soldiers%20but%20also%20causing%20severe%20disruptions%20in%20military%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20servicewoman%20%26quot%3BKira%26quot%3B%20vividly%20recounted%20a%20%26quot%3Bmouse%20epidemic%26quot%3B%20that%20plagued%20her%20battalion%20in%20the%20southern%20Zaporizhzhia%20region%20last%20fall.%20She%20described%20the%20unsettling%20scenario%20of%20soldiers%20trying%20to%20rest%2C%20only%20to%20be%20disturbed%20by%20mice%20crawling%20into%20their%20clothing%2C%20biting%20fingers%2C%20and%20causing%20sleepless%20nights.%20In%20Kira's%20dugout%2C%20housing%20four%20soldiers%2C%20the%20estimated%201%2C000%20mice%20turned%20the%20tables%2C%20making%20the%20soldiers%20feel%20like%20guests%20in%20their%20own%20quarters%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20infestation%20is%20attributed%20to%20seasonal%20changes%2C%20the%20mating%20cycle%20of%20mice%2C%20and%20the%20stagnant%20nature%20of%20the%20war.%20Ukraine's%20counteroffensive%20faced%20strong%20resistance%20from%20heavily%20fortified%20Russian%20defences%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20protracted%20conflict.%20The%20nearly%201%2C000-kilometer%20frontline%20has%20become%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20mice%2C%20spreading%20disease%20and%20discontent%20among%20troops%20searching%20for%20food%20and%20warmth%20in%20the%20bitter%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKira%20and%20her%20fellow%20soldiers%20employed%20various%20methods%2C%20from%20poison%20to%20prayer%2C%20to%20rid%20their%20bunkers%20of%20mice.%20However%2C%20the%20relentless%20influx%20forced%20them%20to%20explore%20unconventional%20strategies.%20Even%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20cat%20named%20Busia%2C%20initially%20effective%20in%20catching%20mice%2C%20proved%20futile%20in%20the%20face%20of%20overwhelming%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%20by%20Ukrainian%20and%20Russian%20soldiers%20provided%20a%20visual%20testament%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20infestation.%20Mice%20and%20rats%20were%20captured%20scurrying%20under%20beds%2C%20in%20backpacks%2C%20power%20generators%2C%20coat%20pockets%2C%20and%20pillowcases.%20The%20severity%20of%20the%20problem%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20mice%20poured%20forth%20from%20a%20Russian%20mortar%20turret%2C%20resembling%20bullets%20from%20a%20Browning%20machine%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Ukraine's%20military%20intelligence%20reported%20an%20outbreak%20of%20%26quot%3Bmouse%20fever%26quot%3B%20among%20Russian%20units%20near%20Kupiansk%20in%20the%20Kharkiv%20region.%20While%20CNN%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20the%20report%2C%20the%20disease%20was%20described%20as%20being%20transmitted%20from%20mice%20to%20humans%20through%20inhalation%20of%20mouse%20feces%20dust%20or%20ingestion%20of%20mouse%20feces%20in%20food.%20Symptoms%20included%20fevers%2C%20rashes%2C%20low%20blood%20pressure%2C%20eye%20hemorrhages%2C%20vomiting%2C%20severe%20back%20pain%2C%20and%20urinary%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20Defence%20Intelligence%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bmouse%20fever%26quot%3B%20significantly%20reduced%20the%20combat%20capability%20of%20Russian%20soldiers%2C%20highlighting%20the%20debilitating%20impact%20of%20the%20infestation.%20The%20specific%20condition%20affecting%20Russian%20troops%20was%20not%20named%2C%20but%20various%20diseases%20associated%20with%20living%20near%20rodents%20could%20present%20similar%20symptoms%2C%20including%20tularemia%2C%20leptospirosis%2C%20and%20hantavirus%2C%20according%20to%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20draws%20parallels%20with%20World%20War%20I%2C%20where%20%26quot%3Btrench%20rats%26quot%3B%20thrived%20in%20unsanitary%20conditions%2C%20causing%20immense%20stress%20for%20soldiers.%20The%20rat%20population%20surged%20during%20periods%20of%20conflict%20stagnation%2C%20and%20concerns%20arose%20that%20a%20similar%20pattern%20is%20emerging%20in%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20General%20Valery%20Zaluzhny%2C%20head%20of%20Ukraine's%20armed%20forces%2C%20drew%20parallels%20with%20the%20technological%20stalemate%20of%20the%20first%20world%20war%2C%20emphasising%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIhor%20Zahorodniuk%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20Ukraine's%20National%20Museum%20of%20National%20History%2C%20attributed%20the%20mouse%20infestation%20to%20rodent%20reproduction%20peaks%20in%20the%20fall%20and%20the%20disruptive%20effects%20of%20the%20war%20itself.%20Winter%20crops%20sown%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202021%20were%20left%20unharvested%20in%20many%20places%20in%202022%2C%20providing%20an%20ideal%20environment%20for%20mice%20to%20breed.%20The%20dispersal%20of%20natural%20predators%20further%20facilitated%20their%20propagation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20causing%20anxiety%20and%20disease%20among%20soldiers%2C%20mice%20have%20devastated%20military%20and%20electrical%20equipment.%20Kira%2C%20while%20working%20as%20a%20signalman%20in%20Zaporizhzhia%2C%20recounted%20how%20mice%20infiltrated%20metal%20boxes%2C%20chewing%20through%20wires%20and%20disrupting%20communications.%20The%20financial%20losses%20incurred%20from%20the%20damage%20were%20significant%2C%20amounting%20to%20one%20million%20hryvnia%20(USD%2026%2C500)%20in%20her%20dugout%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ukraine%20faces%20another%20harsh%20winter%2C%20the%20mouse%20problem%20is%20expected%20to%20intensify.%20Zahorodniuk%20warned%20that%20colder%20temperatures%20would%20drive%20mice%20into%20trenches%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20situation.%20He%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20organised%20efforts%20to%20combat%20the%20infestation%2C%20emphasising%20the%20impact%20on%20the%20combat%20capability%20of%20the%20army%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705850700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fnf60snqo