0was%20attacked%20at%20Jumugurihat%20in%20Sunitpur%20by%20%E2%80%9Can%20unruly%20BJP%20crowd%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20president%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20was%20scathing%20about%20Sarma%2C%20when%20he%20along%20with%20Gandhi%20addressed%20a%20public%20meeting%20at%20Nagaon.%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNowadays%20in%20Assam%2C%20those%20who%20left%20us%20and%20joined%20BJP%20are%20the%20%E2%80%98new%20converted%20CMs%E2%80%99.%20They%20are%20threatening%20us.%20BJP%20people%20also%20attacked%20the%20Yatra%20and%20broke%20the%20glass%20panes%20of%20the%20vehicles.%20Poster%2FBanner%20also%20torn.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20bow%20before%20the%20British%2C%20then%20how%20will%20we%20bow%20before%20the%20BJP%3F%20The%20CM%20here%20forgets%20that%20he%20himself%20is%20accused%20of%20countless%20scams%2C%20cases%20are%20registered%20under%20many%20sections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CRahul%20Ji%20rightly%20said%20that%20the%20CM%20of%20Assam%20is%20the%20most%20corrupt%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20country.%20If%20today%20they%20are%20being%20honest%20and%20clean%2C%20then%20it%20is%20only%20because%20of%20the%20wonder%20of%20Modi%20ji%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20ji%E2%80%99s%20washing%20machine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Assam%20CM%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20gone%20onto%20say%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20avoid%20visiting%20Batadrawa%20Than%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Vaishnavite%20saint%20Srimanta%20Sankardeva%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fassam%2Frahul-to-visit-assamese-icon-sankardevas-birthplace-on-jan-22-as-scheduled-congress-2858237%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20maintained%20that%20Gandhi%20will%20visit%20the%20Than%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%2