d%20for%20centuries%20to%20Hindus%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20grand%20Ram%20temple%2C%20even%20as%20it%20recognised%20the%20illegality%20of%20the%201992%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20these%20two%20events%20%E2%80%93%20the%20December%206%20vandalism%20and%20the%20protracted%20legal%20battle%20over%20the%20title%20of%20the%20land%20%E2%80%93%20that%20eventually%20created%20the%20conditions%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20to%20be%20held%20on%20January%2022%2C%20an%20event%20to%20be%20presided%20over%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20amid%20unprecedented%20state%20intervention%20in%20an%20ostensibly%20Hindu%20religious%20event.%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20leader%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20key%20accused%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%2C%20is%20today%20the%20main%20coordinator%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20event%20in%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%2C%20a%20special%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20court%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20September%2030%2C%202020%20acquitted%20all%2032%20living%20accused%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20conspiracy%20case.%20Most%20of%20the%20accused%20persons%20were%20linked%20to%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20the%20VHP%2C%20which%20are%20affiliates%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20socio-political%20outfit%2C%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20BJP%20leaders%20L.K.%20Advani%20(former%20deputy%20prime%20minister)%2C%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%2C%20Vinay%20Katiyar%20and%20former%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Kalyan%20Singh%2C%20under%20whose%20watch%20the%20mosque%20was%20demolished%2C%20were%20among%20those%20charged%20and%20acquitted.%20Two%20Muslim%20litigants%20from%20Ayodhya%2C%20Haji%20Mehboob%20and%20Syed%20Akhlaq%20Ahmad%2C%20whose%20property%20was%20also%20vandalised%20in%20the%20violence%20unleashed%20by%20karsevaks%20in%20the%20hours%20following%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20approached%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20against%20the%20CBI%20court%20judgment.%20But%20on%20November%209%2C%202022%2C%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20dismissed%20their%20appeal.%20The%20high%20court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Ramesh%20Sinha%20and%20Saroj%20Yadav%20ruled%20that%20since%20Mehboob%20and%20Ahmad%20could%20not%20be%20defined%20as%20%E2%80%98victims%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20had%20no%20locus%20to%20challenge%20the%20CBI%20court%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20seems%20to%20have%20died%20there%2C%20as%20this%20was%20not%20challenged%20in%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20according%20to%20lawyers%20concerned%20with%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehboob%20was%20not%20available%20for%20comment.%20M.R.%20Shamshad%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20part%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20cases%20in%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20said%20Mehboob%20decided%20against%20approaching%20theSupreme%20Court%20to%20challenge%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20dismissal%20of%20the%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20opined%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20purpose%20served%20in%20going%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shamshad%2C%20stressing%20that%20their%20work%20was%20to%20support%20and%20help%20litigants%20whose%20locus%20could%20have%20been%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20All-India%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20had%20in%202022%20said%20it%20would%20challenge%20the%20high%20court%20dismissal%20of%20the%20appeal.%20But%20when%20AIMPLB%20spokesperson%20S.Q.R.%20Ilyas%20was%20asked%20about%20this%2C%20he%20could%20not%20confirm%20if%20such%20an%20appeal%20had%20been%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ER.K.%20Yadav%2C%20the%20CBI%20counsel%20who%20argued%20for%20the%20prosecution%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20trial%2C%20said%20that%20as%20per%20his%20knowledge%2C%20the%20CBI%20did%20not%20file%20an%20appeal%20against%20the%202020%20judgment.%20%E2%80%9COur%20opinion%20was%20sought%20and%20we%20sent%20it%20to%20the%20CBI.%20After%20that%20we%20were%20out%20of%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%202020%20acquittal%20in%20the%20Lucknow%20court%20brought%20a%20closure%20to%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20case%2C%20the%20matter%20had%20stretched%20almost%20three%20decades%20in%20different%20courts%20of%20UP.%20On%20December%206%2C%201992%2C%20lakhs%20of%20karsevaks%20had%20assembled%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Around%20noon%20that%20day%2C%20armed%20with%20spades%2C%20shovels%2C%20ropes%2C%20axes%20and%20other%20equipment%2C%20the%20frenzied%20mob%20of%20karsevaks%20breached%20barriers%20set%20up%20by%20the%20police%20and%20entered%20the%20Ram%20Chabutra%20in%20front%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20eventually%20climbed%20atop%20the%20mosque.%20Police%20fired%20tear%20gas%20shells%20at%20the%20mob%20but%20it%20did%20not%20have%20any%20impact%20on%20them%2C%20as%20they%20had%20applied%20%E2%80%9Cfacepacks%20and%20chemicals%E2%80%9D%20on%20their%20faces%2C%20the%20CBI%20submitted%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ayodhya%3A%20The%20Sordid%20Timeline%20Leading%20to%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Consecration%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-the-sordid-timeline-leading-to-the-ram-temple-consecration%5C%22%3EAyodhya%3A%20The%20Sordid%20Timeline%20Leading%20to%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Consecration%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20karsevaks%20soon%20turned%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20to%20dust.%20A%20total%20of%2049%20FIRs%20were%20filed%20after%20the%20incident%20but%20the%20CBI%20trial%20dealt%20with%20two%20main%20crimes%20concerning%20the%20demolition%20and%20the%20conspiracy%20behind%20it.%20The%20first%20FIR%20(no.%20197)%20was%20lodged%20by%20the%20police%20at%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20police%20station%20against%20unnamed%20kar%20sevaks%20on%20the%20charges%20of%20dacoity%2C%20robbery%2C%20causing%20hurt%2C%20injuring%20and%20defiling%20place%20of%20worship%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20FIR%20(no.%20198)%20was%20lodged%20against%20eight%20persons%2C%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%2C%20Vinay%20Katiyar%2C%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20Sadhvi%20Ritambhara%2C%20Ashok%20Singhal%2C%20Giriraj%20Kishore%20and%20V.H.%20Dalmia%20on%20the%20allegation%20of%20inciting%20the%20violent%20act%20through%20their%20provocative%20speeches%20and%20exhortations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20eventual%20main%20charge%20of%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20they%20also%20faced%20charges%20of%20rioting%2C%20unlawful%20assembly%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20and%20delivering%20imputations%2C%20assertions%20prejudicial%20to%20national%20integration%20and%20statements%20conducing%20to%20public%20mischief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20FIRs%20were%20lodged%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20journalists%20who%20were%20attacked%20by%20karsevaks%20and%20suffered%20damage%20to%20their%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFIR%20197%20against%20the%20karsevaks%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI%20on%20December%2013%2C%201992.%20The%20FIR%20against%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20leaders%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20CB-CID%20of%20UP%20on%20December%2010%2C%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2016%2C%201992%2C%20the%20state%20of%20UP%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20high%20court%20established%20a%20special%20court%20of%20judicial%20magistrate%20class%20I%20at%20Lalitpur%20to%20try%20the%20FIR%20198.%20On%20July%208%2C%201993%2C%20the%20state%20government%20shifted%20the%20place%20of%20sitting%20of%20the%20court%20from%20Lalitpur%20to%20Rae%20Bareli.%20The%20Union%20government%2C%20with%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%20on%20August%2026%2C%201993%20handed%20over%20the%20probe%20of%20the%20FIR%20number%20198%20to%20the%20CBI.%20The%20CBI%20took%20charge%20of%20all%2049%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%208%2C%201993%2C%20the%20state%20government%20established%20a%20special%20court%20of%20additional%20chief%20judicial%20magistrate%20at%20Lucknow%20for%20trial%20of%20the%20cases%20of%20the%20demolition%20investigated%20by%20the%20CBI.%20The%20case%20against%20the%20Sangh%20leaders%20was%20being%20heard%20in%20Rae%20Bareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20April%202017%20used%20its%20extraordinary%20constitutional%20powers%20under%20Article%20142%20to%20restore%20the%20criminal%20conspiracy%20charges%20framed%20against%20Advani%20and%20others%2C%20overruling%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20decision%20of%202010%20to%20drop%20the%20conspiracy%20charges%20against%20them.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20upheld%20a%20CBI%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20drop%20the%20conspiracy%20charges%20against%20Advani%20and%20others%20in%202001.%20Following%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directions%2C%20the%20special%20CBI%20court%20in%20Lucknow%20in%202017%20framed%20charges%20under%20criminal%20conspiracy%20against%20Advani%20and%20several%20other%20accused%2C%20most%20of%20them%20linked%20to%20the%20Sangh%20parivar.%20The%20apex%20court%20also%20transferred%20the%20Rae%20Bareli%20trial%20and%20clubbed%20it%20with%20the%20Lucknow%20case%20pending%20before%20a%20CBI%20Special%20Court.%20A%20comprehensive%20trial%20was%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20351%20prosecution%20witnesses%2C%20including%20many%20journalists%20who%20covered%20the%20demolition%2C%20were%20examined%20by%20the%20court.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20three%20decades%2C%20many%20witnesses%20died%20or%20were%20too%20old%20or%20frail%20to%20appear%20in%20court.%20Kalyan%20Singh%20was%20the%20only%20accused%20to%20submit%20documentary%20evidence%20in%20his%20defence.%20The%20accused%20persons%20did%20not%20produce%20a%20single%20witness%20in%20their%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2030%2C%202020%20special%20judge%20S.K.%20Yadav%2C%20in%20a%20%2C2300-page%20judgment%2C%20acquitted%20Advani%2C%20Kalyan%20Singh%20and%2030%20others%20for%20lack%20of%20credible%20evidence.%20Just%20seven%20months%20after%20that%20verdict%2C%20also%20his%20last%20working%20day%2C%20retired%20judge%20Yadav%20was%20appointed%20as%20a%20deputy%20Lokayukta%20in%20UP%20by%20the%20Adityanath-led%20state%20government.%20Incidentally%2C%20Yadav%20had%20started%20and%20ended%20his%20legal%20career%20from%20the%20same%20district%2C%20Faizabad%2C%20now%20renamed%20Ayodhya.%20In%20June%201990%2C%20he%20started%20his%20career%20as%20an%20additional%20munsif%20in%20Faizabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20rejected%20the%20charges%20of%20criminal%20conspiracy%20levelled%20against%20the%20accused%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20chargesheet%20did%20not%20have%20any%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Cgot%20together%20in%20common%20intent%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20group%20of%20%E2%80%9Chooligan%20karsevaks%E2%80%9D%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20mosque.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20judge%20went%20on%20to%20observe%20that%20a%20group%20of%20unruly%20karsevaks%20had%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20sudden%20agitation%20indulged%20in%20violence%20even%20as%20senior%20VHP%20leader%20Ashok%20Singhal%20had%20appealed%20them%20to%20retreat.%20The%20evidence%20submitted%20in%20court%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20form%20of%20newspaper%20clippings%2C%20video%20cassettes%2C%20tape%20records%2C%20printed%20material%2C%20speeches%20and%20witness%20testimonies%20made%20it%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20that%20there%20was%20no%20moment%20when%20the%20accused%20persons%20gathered%20in%20a%20room%20to%20plan%20the%20scheme%20to%20demolish%20the%20structure%E2%80%9D%2C%20ruled%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20credible%E2%80%9D%20of%20some%20witnesses%20to%20point%20to%20some%20accused%20and%20say%20that%20they%20were%20exhorting%20karsevaks%20to%20demolish%20the%20mosque%2C%20as%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20dust%20inside%20the%20complex%20which%20was%20filled%20with%20lakhs%20of%20karsevaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disputed%20structure%20was%20about%20200-300%20metres%20away%20from%20the%20Katha%20Kunj%20dias%2C%20where%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20leaders%20were%20seated%2C%20but%20some%20witnesses%20had%20said%20it%20was%20800%20metres%20away%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20several%20Muslims%20in%20and%20outside%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20Babri%20demolition%20judgment%20was%20a%20moment%20where%20they%20hoped%20that%20the%20court%20would%20provide%20them%20some%20solace%20in%20the%20form%20of%20justice.%20However%2C%20the%20criminal%20act%20of%20December%206%2C%201992%20went%20unpunished%20by%20law.%20Many%20of%20the%20accused%20went%20on%20to%20become%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20with%20the%20now%20ruling%20BJP%20over%20the%20course%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhaliq%20Ahmad%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20and%20convenor%20of%20the%20Faizabad%20Hilal%20Committee%2C%20who%20has%20closely%20tracked%20the%20Babri%20demolition%20and%20its%20aftermath%2C%20says%20the%20CBI%20court%20failed%20to%20provide%20justice.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20act%20was%20committed%20in%20front%20of%20the%20entire%20world.%20There%20were%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20the%20demolition%20that%20were%20published.%20What%20can%20we%20say%2C%20if%20everyone%20decided%20to%20turn%20deaf%20and%20blind%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ahmad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20also%20blames%20the%20Muslim%20intelligentsia%20and%20bodies%20for%20not%20pursuing%20the%20demolition%20case%20with%20more%20diligence%2C%20Ahmad%20consigns%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20verdict%20following%20the%20title%20suit%20judgment%20to%20be%20the%20last%20injury%20caused%20to%20the%20collective%20conscience%20of%20Muslims%20in%20recent%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20our%20body%20gets%20one%20wound%2C%20we%20can%20pinpoint%20where%20the%20pain%20is%20emanating%20from.%20But%20when%20the%20entire%20body%20is%20wounded%2C%20how%20can%20we%20identify%20where%20it%20actually%20hurts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705841711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F04164827%2Fpic_8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-babri-masjid-demolition-went-unpunished-and-the-fight-for-justice-died%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%202022%20decision%20to%20acquit%20all%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20conspiracy%20case%20%E2%80%93%20including%20senior%20BJP%20and%20VHP%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20was%20never%20appealed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-babri-masjid-demolition-went-unpunished-and-the-fight-for-justice-died%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%20govt%20threatening%20people%20not%20to%20join%20Cong%20yatra%2C%20says%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705841683000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F17%2Ffull%2F1697533187-4203.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fassam-govt-threatening-people-not-to-join-cong-yatra-says-rahul-gandhi-124012100372_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20also%20said%20the%20Congress%20will%20win%20by%20a%20huge%20margin%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fassam-govt-threatening-people-not-to-join-cong-yatra-says-rahul-gandhi-124012100372_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fpolitics%2Fassam-govt-threatening-people-not-to-join-cong-yatra-says-rahul-gandhi-124012100372_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fpolitics%2Fassam-govt-threatening-people-not-to-join-cong-yatra-says-rahul-gandhi-124012100372_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSitting%20At%20Home%20For%203%20Months%26quot%3B%3A%20Delhi%20Pollution%20Eats%20Up%20Informal%20Jobs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESaroj%2C%20a%2055-year-old%20construction%20worker%20residing%20near%20the%20Bakkarwala%20landfill%20site%2C%20embodies%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20informal%20sector%20workers%20amid%20the%20escalating%20air%20pollution%20crisis%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20frequent%20construction%20bans%20to%20combat%20air%20pollution%2C%20Saroj%20found%20herself%20periodically%20unemployed%20for%20the%20past%20three%20months%2C%20grappling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20like%20her%2C%20whose%20primary%20income%20source%20is%20construction%20work%2C%20the%20shutdown%20presents%20a%20formidable%20financial%20setback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20no%20stable%20construction%20work%20since%20October%20(Diwali)%20and%20we%20have%20been%20sitting%20at%20home%20for%20three%20months%20now.%20The%20contractor%20informs%20us%20that%20work%20will%20only%20resume%20in%20a%20few%20months%20when%20the%20air%20pollution%20situation%20improves%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20the%20construction%20industry%2C%20despite%20its%20polluting%20nature%2C%20has%20become%20an%20unavoidable%20necessity%20for%20these%20workers%2C%20exposing%20them%20to%20some%20of%20the%20most%20severe%20health%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFever%2C%20cough%20and%20cold%20and%20stomach%20issues%20are%20very%20common%20for%20us%20living%20close%20to%20and%20working%20on%20construction%20sites%2C%26quot%3B%20Saroj%20said%2C%20shedding%20light%20on%20the%20health%20challenges%20she%20endures%20due%20to%20persistent%20exposure%20to%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20recorded%20its%20worst%20December%20in%20terms%20of%20air%20quality%20in%202023.%20The%20city's%20average%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20for%20the%20month%20was%20at%20348%2C%20the%20highest%20since%202018%20when%20it%20had%20reached%20360.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20Stage%20III%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20that%20involves%20a%20complete%20halt%20on%20construction%20and%20demolition%20work%2C%20except%20for%20essential%20government%20projects%20in%20Delhi%20and%20surrounding%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20survey%20conducted%20by%20Help%20Delhi%20Breathe%20and%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20revealed%20that%20informal%20workers%20such%20as%20Saroj%2C%20particularly%20those%20residing%20near%20landfill%20sites%20in%20Delhi%2C%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20adverse%20effects%20of%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20workers%20grapple%20with%20challenges%2C%20including%20heightened%20exposure%20to%20outdoor%20activities%2C%20unfavourable%20working%20and%20living%20conditions%2C%20hazardous%20work%20sites%20and%20social%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20informal%20sector%20faces%20a%20significant%20blow%20to%20livelihoods%20due%20to%20a%20confluence%20of%20issues%20such%20as%20extreme%20cold%2C%20air%20pollution%2C%20heat%20stress%2C%20lack%20of%20green%20spaces%2C%20waste%20burning%20and%20open%20drainage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%2042%20per%20cent%20of%20respondents%20in%20the%20survey%20expressed%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20government%20should%20abstain%20from%20shutting%20down%20polluting%20companies%2C%20emphasising%20the%20imperative%20of%20preserving%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20covered%20590%20informal%20sector%20workers%20across%20Bakkarwala%2C%20Gokulpuri%2C%20Sawda%20Ghevra%2C%20Nand%20Nagri%20and%20Bhalswa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstruction%20workers%20comprised%20the%20majority%20of%20informal%20settlement%20residents%20surveyed%20at%2046.6%20per%20cent%2C%20followed%20by%20waste%20pickers%20at%2010.2%20per%20cent%20and%20street%20vendors%20at%206.9%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20revealed%20that%20the%20closure%20of%20construction%20sites%20not%20only%20results%20in%20job%20losses%20but%20also%20engenders%20uncertainty%20for%20these%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2077%20per%20cent%2C%20a%20substantial%20majority%20of%20respondents%20pointed%20to%20an%20inherent%20conflict%20between%20economic%20development%20and%20environmental%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2091%20per%20cent%20reported%20falling%20sick%20due%20to%20deteriorating%20air%20quality.%20The%20survey%20further%20highlighted%20that%2095%20per%20cent%20of%20workers%20refrained%20from%20raising%20pollution%20concerns%20at%20their%20workplaces%2C%20primarily%20due%20to%20the%20fear%20of%20job%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstant%20exposure%20to%20pollution%20and%20excessively%20long%20working%20hours%20emerged%20as%20top%20workplace%20concerns%20for%2075%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20respondents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20workers%20implement%20preventive%20measures%20at%20home%20and%20underscore%20the%20need%20for%20protective%20equipment%20for%20workplace%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20construction%20activities%20are%20halted%20during%20high%20air%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20recognise%20how%20it%20impacts%20the%20already%20precarious%20livelihood%20and%20financial%20security%20of%20informal%20sector%20workers.%20Help%20Delhi%20Breathe%20and%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20are%20diligently%20working%20to%20raise%20awareness%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20connect%20workers%20to%20social%20security%20schemes%20that%20can%20safeguard%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gurpriya%20Singh%2C%20a%20campaigner%20affiliated%20with%20Help%20Delhi%20Breathe%2C%20a%20citizen-led%20collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahila%20Housing%20Trust%20Director%20Bijal%20Brahmbhatt%20underscored%20the%20severe%20health%20challenges%20faced%20by%20informal%20sector%20workers%20due%20to%20Delhi's%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaste%20pickers%20at%20settlements%20such%20as%20Bhalswa%20are%20grappling%20with%20additional%20health%20issues%2C%20including%20contaminated%20water%2C%20toxic%20fumes%20from%20garbage%20burning%2C%20and%20handling%20toxic%20waste%20without%20adequate%20protective%20equipment%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Brahmbhatt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Brahmbhatt%20emphasised%20the%20necessity%20for%20precise%20measures%2C%20including%20skill%20development%20and%20training%20programmes%2C%20to%20provide%20alternative%20employment%20opportunities%20and%20reduce%20dependence%20on%20waste-picking%20for%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Singh%20of%20Help%20Delhi%20Breathe%20pointed%20out%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20issue%20where%20industry%20shutdowns%2C%20aimed%20at%20combating%20air%20pollution%2C%20end%20up%20disproportionately%20affecting%20workers%20who%20contribute%20the%20least%20to%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20pattern%20is%20observed%20not%20only%20in%20Delhi%20but%20across%20states%2C%20particularly%20in%20construction%20and%20brick%20kiln%20industries%2C%20Ms%20Singh%20said.%20She%20emphasised%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20women%20workers%2C%20who%20often%20bear%20additional%20burdens%20such%20as%20childcare%20at%20construction%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20workers%20are%20all%20the%20more%20impacted%20due%20to%20burdens%20of%20childcare%20at%20sites.%20They%20are%20usually%20assigned%20unskilled%20tasks%20and%20are%20paid%20less%20than%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20women%20tend%20to%20be%20the%20last%20to%20seek%20health%20care%2C%20further%20compounding%20their%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20health%20needs%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20context%20of%20air%20pollution%20impacts%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoshini%20Suparna%20Diwakar%2C%20a%20senior%20consultant%20with%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%2C%20underlined%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20take%20action%20to%20protect%20construction%20workers%20from%20the%20hazardous%20nature%20of%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimple%20solutions%20such%20as%20providing%20masks%2C%20sprinkling%20water%20and%20ensuring%20water%20and%20sanitation%20facilities%20can%20contribute%20significantly%20to%20the%20overall%20wellbeing%20of%20workers%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiwakar%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20looking%20at%20the%20issue%20holistically%2C%20with%20specific%20attention%20to%20implementing%20guidelines%20such%20as%20creche%20facilities%20to%20protect%20children%20from%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705841520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fbft343d8_delhi-pollution_650x400_12_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-crisis-sitting-at-home-for-3-months-delhi-pollution-eats-up-informal-jobs-4904412%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saroj%2C%20a%2055-year-old%20construction%20worker%20residing%20near%20the%20Bakkarwala%20landfill%20site%2C%20embodies%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20informal%20sector%20workers%20amid%20the%20escalating%20air%20pollution%20crisis%20in%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-crisis-sitting-at-home-for-3-months-delhi-pollution-eats-up-informal-job