unjab%20province).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20was%20speaking%20at%20a%20religious%20function%20at%20Bairagarh%20near%20Bhopal.%20He%20said%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20is%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20a%20%E2%80%9CRam%20Rajya%20(ideal%20state)%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20possible%20recovery%20from%20the%20losses%20made%20by%20India%20after%20the%20partition%20in%201947%20when%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20lost%20Sindh%2C%20Punjab%20was%20divided%2C%20and%20Pakistan%20was%20formed%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fakhand-bharat-will-happen-one-day-says-mp-cm%2Farticle67760103.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20added%20that%20King%20Vikramaditya%20built%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20temple%20but%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthorn%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20enemies%E2%80%9D%20who%20destroyed%20it.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20being%20reconstructed%20after%20a%20political%20struggle%20of%2030-32%20years.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20for%20the%20last%20500%20years%2C%20several%20generations%20passed%20in%20it%20(the%20struggle)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20president%20V.D.%20Sharma%20made%20a%20similar%20speech%20where%20he%20said%20if%20given%20a%20chance%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20will%20also%20change%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cgeography%E2%80%9D.%20Sharma%20urged%20people%20to%20give%20the%20BJP%20another%20chance%20at%20the%20Centre%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20saffron%20flag%20is%20hoisted%20in%20Lahore%20and%20Karachi.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20one%20who%20is%20building%20a%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20one%20who%20is%20building%20the%20corridor%20of%20Baba%20Vishwanath%2C%20has%20removed%20Article%20370.%20Give%20us%20another%20chance%2C%20we%20will%20show%20you%20by%20changing%20the%20geography%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%