0software%20engineer%20was%20discovered%20covered%20in%20blood%20following%20an%20alleged%20murder%20of%20his%20wife%20in%20their%20California%20home.%20Chen%2C%20a%20former%20employee%20of%20Google%2C%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20murder.%20The%20incident%20highlighted%20the%20depth%20and%20destructiveness%20of%20domestic%20violence%20deaths.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fgoogle-engineer-found-spattered-in-blood-after-alleged-murder-of-wife%2Farticleshow%2F107025372.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fgoogle-engineer-found-spattered-in-blood-after-alleged-murder-of-wife%2Famp_articleshow%2F107025372.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fgoogle-engineer-found-spattered-in-blood-after-alleged-murder-of-wife%2Famp_articleshow%2F107025372.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netflix's%20Quick%20Capitulation%20in%20Pulling%20Down%20'Annapoorani'%20Sets%20a%20Grim%20Precedent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21113530%2F407290882_889094969512509_8484544877523113598_n.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Nilesh%20Krishnaa%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EAnnapoorani%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Nayanthara%20plays%20the%20protagonist%2C%20belonging%20to%20a%20Brahmin%20family.%20Her%20father%2C%20who%20we%E2%80%99re%20told%20is%20an%20engineer%20by%20qualification%2C%20serves%20as%20the%20cook%20for%20a%20temple%20in%20Srirangam%20(in%20Trichy%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu).%20When%20she%E2%80%99s%20born%2C%20the%20doctor%20observes%20her%20taste%20buds%20are%20superior%20and%20that%20she%20has%20better%20instincts%20about%20flavour.%20It%E2%80%99s%20established%20in%20an%20opening%20montage%20that%20she%20has%20a%20gift%2C%20and%20will%20grow%20up%20to%20be%20a%20famous%20chef.%20Her%20father%20disapproves%20of%20her%20culinary%20ambition%2C%20because%20training%20as%20a%20chef%20would%20mean%20having%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20cook%20meat.%20She%20finds%20a%20way%20to%20overcome%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20disapproval%2C%20and%20elopes%20from%20her%20wedding%20to%20pursue%20her%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnaa%E2%80%99s%20film%20had%20potential%20in%20its%20story%2C%20but%20is%20a%20silly%20star-vehicle%20at%20best%2C%20which%20got%20its%20theatrical%20release%20on%20December%201.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20profile%20has%20grown%20considerably%20across%20the%20country%20after%20it%20was%20pulled%20down%20from%20Netflix%20on%20January%2011%2C%20two%20weeks%20after%20it%20dropped%20on%20the%20platform.%20The%20film%20disappeared%20from%20the%20platform%20a%20few%20days%20after%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20was%20filed%20against%20the%20makers%20for%20%E2%80%9Churting%20Hindu%20sentiments%E2%80%9D%20by%20a%20certain%20Ramesh%20Solanki%20%E2%80%93%20a%20former%20Shiv%20Sena%20member%2C%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20Hindu%20IT%20Wing%20on%20January%208.%20Another%20complaint%20was%20filed%20by%20VHP%20activist%20Arup%20Mukherjee%20on%20January%2011%2C%20for%20%E2%80%9Churting%20Hindu%20sentiments%20and%20for%20promoting%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%E2%80%99s%20teaser%20created%20quite%20a%20stir%20on%20social%20media%2C%20showing%20Nayanthara%E2%80%99s%20character%20reading%20a%20kebab%20recipe%20juxtaposed%20with%20her%20Hindu%20father%20praying.%20Many%20social%20media%20users%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20reacted%20strongly%20to%20how%20Hinduism%20was%20being%20%E2%80%98disrespected%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20teaser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20questionnaire%20around%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20disappearance%20from%20the%20platform%2C%20a%20Netflix%20spokesperson%20responded%20with%20the%20following%20statement%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CThe%20film%20has%20been%20removed%20at%20the%20licensor%E2%80%99s%20request.%E2%80%9D%20When%20probed%20further%2C%20the%20streaming%20giant%20elaborated%20it%20was%20a%20licensor%20called%20Mango%20Mass%20Media%20who%20had%20taken%20the%20call%20to%20remove%20the%20film.%20The%20licensor%20even%20tweeted%20about%20it%20on%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20their%20X%20account.%20We%20tried%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20Mango%20Mass%20Media%20several%20times%2C%20but%20they%20remained%20unavailable%20for%20a%20comment.%20So%20did%20director%20Nilesh%20Krishnaa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2018%2C%20actor%20Nayanthara%20shared%20a%20statement%20that%20began%20with%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%20The%20statement%20reads%20as%20follows%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20writing%20this%20note%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%20and%20a%20genuine%20desire%20to%20address%20the%20recent%20turn%20of%20events%20concerning%20our%20film%2C%20%3Cem%3EAnnapoorani%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Crafting%20%3Cem%3EAnnapoorani%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20not%20just%20a%20cinematic%20endeavour%20but%20a%20heartfelt%20pursuit%20of%20inspiring%20resilience%20and%20instilling%20the%20spirit%20of%20never%20giving%20up.%20It%20aimed%20to%20mirror%20life%E2%80%99s%20journey%2C%20where%20we%20learn%20that%20obstacles%20can%20be%20overcome%20with%20sheer%20willpower.%20In%20our%20sincere%20attempt%20to%20share%20a%20positive%20message%2C%20we%20may%20have%20inadvertently%20caused%20hurt.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20note%2C%20the%2039-year-old%20actor%20said%20she%20was%20surprised%20that%20a%20film%20certified%20by%20the%20CBFC%2C%20one%20that%20also%20had%20a%20theatrical%20run%2C%20was%20suddenly%20pulled%20down%20from%20a%20streaming%20platform.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20team%20and%20I%20never%20intended%20to%20hurt%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20sentiments%20and%20we%20understand%20the%20gravity%20of%20this%20issue.%20Being%20someone%20who%20wholly%20believes%20in%20God%20and%20frequently%20visits%20temples%20across%20the%20country%2C%20it%20is%20the%20last%20thing%20I%20would%20intentionally%20do.%20To%20those%20whose%20feelings%20we%E2%80%99ve%20touched%2C%20I%20extend%20my%20sincere%20and%20heartfelt%20apologies%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disappearance%20of%20%3Cem%3EAnnapoorani%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20a%20streaming%20service%20is%20hardly%20the%20first%20time%20a%20film%2Fshow%20has%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%20after%20a%20few%20stray%20FIRs%20were%20filed%20against%20it.%20Amazon%20Prime%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Ftandav-amazon-prime-saif-ali-khan-review%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETandav%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2020)%3C%2Fa%3E%20remains%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ftandav-makers-to-drop-controversial-scenes-thank-ib-ministry-for-guidance%5C%22%3Ea%20flashpoint%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20creative%20freedom%20on%20OTT%20platforms%20was%20renegotiated.%20With%20Krishnaa%E2%80%99s%20film%2C%20things%20seem%20to%20have%20gone%20a%20step%20further.%20It%20might%20have%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20both%20filmmakers%20and%20streaming%20platforms%20to%20become%20even%20more%20paranoid%2C%20hauling%20up%20lawyers%20to%20go%20a%20step%20further%20and%20start%20anticipating%20FIRs%20for%20all%20possible%20social%2C%20political%20commentary%20and%20anything%20that%20would%20%E2%80%98hurt%E2%80%99%20someone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20look%20at%20the%20two%20specific%20scenes%20in%20the%20Nayanthara%20film%20that%20have%20caused%20this%20social%20media%20outrage%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20scene%2C%20Annapoorani%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20friend%20Farhan%20(played%20by%20Jai)%20quotes%20a%20verse%20from%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20where%20Ram%2C%20Lakshman%20and%20Sita%20were%20said%20to%20have%20survived%20on%20deer%20meat%20during%20their%2014-year%20exile.%20This%20is%20Farhan%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20convincing%20Annapoorani%20to%20touch%20meat%20during%20a%20class%20%E2%80%93%20which%20she%20considers%20will%20make%20her%20impure.%20The%20scene%20talks%20about%20one%E2%80%99s%20agency%20to%20choose%20the%20food%20they%E2%80%99re%20eating%20or%20cooking%2C%20rather%20than%20let%20external%20factors%20like%20religion%20or%20parental%20conditioning%20decide%20for%20them.%20Farhan%20explains%20how%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20makes%20delicious%20biryani%2C%20is%20actually%20a%20vegetarian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20socio-political%20climate%2C%20there%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20those%20who%20are%20quick%20to%20react%20at%20scenes%20like%20this.%20A%20Muslim%20boy%20%E2%80%98coaxing%E2%80%99%20a%20Brahmin%20girl%20to%20eat%20meat%2C%20would%20immediately%20feed%20into%20their%20made%20up%20theories%20of%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20and%20religious%20conversions%20an%20invention%20of%20the%20right-wing%E2%80%99s%20fertile%20imagination.%20Such%20people%20conveniently%20overlook%20Farhan%E2%80%99s%20dialogues%20to%20cherry-pick%20elements%20of%20the%20scene%20and%20share%20them%20as%20memes%20or%20short%20videos%2C%20to%20make%20it%20seem%20misleading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20scene%20is%20in%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20climax%2C%20where%20the%20protagonist%20is%20given%20the%20task%20of%20making%20biryani%2C%20in%20the%20final%20round%20of%20a%20national%20cooking%20competition.%20Having%20lost%20her%20sense%20of%20taste%20because%20of%20an%20accident%2C%20the%20protagonist%20offers%20namaz%20before%20starting%20to%20cook.%20The%20scene%20seems%20to%20be%20implying%20that%20Nayanthara%E2%80%99s%20character%20is%20seeking%20spiritual%20guidance%20at%20a%20crucial%20juncture%20in%20her%20life.%20One%20could%20accuse%20the%20makers%20of%20being%20cheesy%2C%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20all%20there%20is%20to%20it.%20Not%20for%20the%20hyperactive%20minds%20of%20those%20who%20ignore%20the%20context%20of%20seeing%20a%20Brahmin%20girl%20offering%20a%20namaz%2C%20consume%20it%20at%20face%20value%20and%20are%20quick%20to%20take%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20film%20having%20been%20taken%20down%20from%20the%20streaming%20services%20and%20the%20personnel%20associated%20with%20the%20film%20having%20released%20public%20apologies%20to%20the%20complainants%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20likely%20that%20the%20FIRs%20will%20be%20forgotten%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%20However%2C%20it%20does%20set%20a%20dangerous%20precedent%20for%20films%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20While%20Hindi%20films%20have%20been%20watchful%20about%20such%20controversies%2C%20filmmakers%20down%20South%20(especially%20in%20Tamil%2C%20Malayalam)%20were%20able%20to%20slide%20in%20political%2C%20social%20commentary%2C%20without%20the%20fear%20of%20online%20mobs%20or%20the%20establishment.%20That%20dam%20seems%20to%20have%20broken%20with%20%3Cem%3EAnnapoorani%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetflix%20might%20have%20passed%20the%20buck%20for%20%3Cem%3EAnnapoorani%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20removal%20to%20the%20licensor%2C%20but%20filmmaker%20Dibakar%20Banerjee%20has%20mentioned%20in%20more%20than%20one%20interview%20how%20his%20film%20%3Cem%3ETees%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20starring%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%2C%20Neeraj%20Kabi%2C%20Kalki%20Koechlin%2C%20Shashank%20Arora%20and%20Huma%20Qureshi%20%E2%80%93%20commissioned%20by%20Netflix%2C%20will%20not%20be%20released%20by%20the%20streaming%20giant.%20When%20asked%20about%20it%2C%20Netflix%20maintained%20they%20were%20a%20proponent%20of%20creative%20expression.%20They%20shared%20the%20following%20statement%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20an%20incredibly%20broad%20range%20of%20Indian%20original%20films%20and%20TV%20shows%2C%20all%20of%20which%20speak%20to%20our%20long%20standing%20support%20for%20creative%20expression.%20This%20diversity%20not%20only%20reflects%20our%20members%E2%80%99%20very%20different%20tastes%2C%20it%20also%20distinguishes%20our%20service%20from%20the%20competition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Broadcasting%20Services%20(Regulation)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20on%20the%20horizon%20%E2%80%93%20which%20seeks%20to%20bring%20eve