ns%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20has%20made%20this%20unambiguous%20announcement%20without%20any%20hesitation%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F265586%2Ftemple-belongs-to-ramanand-sect-not-to-sanyasis-shaiva-or-shakta-champat-rai-s-remarks-draw-ire%2F%5C%22%3Einterview%20given%20to%20a%20Hindi%20daily%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20leaving%20no%20scope%20of%20doubt%20for%20anyone.%20The%20same%20group%20of%20people%20who%20claimed%20that%20this%20temple%20was%20the%20property%20of%20the%20entire%20nation%20is%20now%20bent%20on%20depriving%20a%20section%20from%20rights%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20this%20trust%20is%20dominated%20by%20members%20hailing%20from%20a%20particular%20caste%2C%20class%20and%20organisation.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20trust%20has%20been%20facing%20allegations%2C%20internally%20and%20externally%2C%20of%20not%20properly%20representing%20the%20sants%20and%20mahants%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20disregarding%20the%20contribution%20of%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20castes%20in%20the%20movement%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20Ram%20temple%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ewahin%20%3C%2Fem%3E(there)%E2%80%99%2C%20overstepping%20its%20boundaries%20and%20indulging%20in%20corruption.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20though%20its%20members%20have%20repeatedly%20praised%20Hindu%20unity%2C%20very%20few%20people%20believed%20that%20the%20trust%20would%20be%20able%20to%20do%20proper%20justice%20to%20the%20pluralism%20prevalent%20among%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20many%20%E2%80%98ungrateful%E2%80%99%20people%20have%20long%20been%20questioning%20the%20remarks%20made%20by%20Champat%20Rai%20and%20asking%20%E2%80%93%20who%20does%20the%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20being%20built%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20the%20trust%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20court%20with%20the%20money%20collected%20from%20Hindu%20devotees%2C%20belong%20to%3F%20Does%20it%20belong%20to%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20who%20kickstarted%20the%20agitation%20for%20it%3F%20Or%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20of%20which%20it%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20organisation%3F%20Or%20all%20Hindus%3F%20Or%20only%20its%20dominant%20and%20elite%20classes%20and%20noblemen%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%3A%20A%20Stage%20for%20the%20Visible%20Display%20of%20BJP's%20Extremely%20Backward%20Class%20Politics%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fayodhyas-ram-temple-a-stage-for-the-visible-display-of-bjps-extremely-backward-class-politics%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20Ram%20Temple%3A%20A%20Stage%20for%20the%20Visible%20Display%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Extremely%20Backward%20Class%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20trust%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F261004%2Fayodhya-ram-mandir-trust-ramanandi-sampraday%2F%5C%22%3Echose%20the%20Ramanandi%20method%20for%20the%20worship%20of%20Ramlala%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20child%20form%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20asked%20why%20this%20choice%20was%20made.%20Was%20it%20because%20this%20sect%20was%20the%20largest%20sect%20of%20Vaishnav%20sadhus%20and%20ascetics%20in%20the%20country%20or%20because%20of%20its%20important%20historical%20role%20in%20establishing%20coordination%20between%20various%20streams%20and%20branches%20of%20Rambhakti%20by%20brushing%20off%20caste%20hatred%3F%20Or%20was%20it%20because%20Ayodhya%20is%20the%20city%20of%20Ramanandis%3F%20Another%20question%20that%20was%20raised%20was%20%E2%80%93%20how%20will%20the%20narrow-minded%20trust%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20customs%20and%20policies%20of%20the%20pluralistic%20Ramanandi%20sect%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20when%20Champat%20Rai%20made%20an%20appeal%20asking%20those%20who%20are%20not%20invited%20by%20his%20trust%20to%20not%20attend%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20on%20January%2022%2C%20the%20question%20arose%20in%20many%20circles%20whether%20it%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98loyal%E2%80%99%20religious%20leaders%2C%20political%20leaders%2C%20acharyas%2C%20dignitaries%2C%20industrialists%2C%20sportspersons%2C%20actors%20and%20artists%20who%20had%20the%20first%20right%20on%20the%20temple%2C%20who%20are%20treated%20as%20VVIPs%20by%20the%20trust%20and%20invited%20to%20the%20Pran%20Pratistha%20purely%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20its%20preference%20and%20not%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20devotion%20towards%20Ram%20or%20their%20faith%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20one%20had%20expected%20that%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20discriminatory%20treatment%20in%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%2C%20the%20impartial%20and%20holy%20god%20and%20the%20one%20who%20provides%20strength%20to%20the%20weak%2C%20Champat%20Rai%20would%20blatantly%20remark%20that%20the%20temple%20does%20not%20belong%20to%20the%20Sanyasis%2C%20Shaivas%20or%20Shaktas%2C%20but%20only%20to%20the%20Ramanandis%20of%20the%20Ramanand%20sect%2C%20giving%20rise%20not%20only%20to%20a%20situation%20of%20%E2%80%98Prathamgrase%20Makshikapatah%E2%80%99%20(things%20soured%20right%20at%20the%20beginning)%20but%20also%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20contradictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20it%20came%20the%20apprehension%20of%20who%20might%20be%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20next.%20What%20is%20the%20guarantee%20that%20those%20who%20are%20the%20chosen%20ones%20now%20will%20continue%20to%20enjoy%20this%20status%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20also%20does%20not%20know%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20the%20system%20of%20coordination%20offered%20by%20Goswami%20Tulsidas%20through%20Ram%20to%20end%20the%20Shaiva-Vaishnav%20conflicts%20of%20the%20past%20(%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ESivadrohi%20Mam%20Das%20Kahwa%2C%20So%20Nar%20Sapnehun%20Mohi%20Na%20Pava%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%2C%20or%20one%20who%20wants%20to%20attain%20me%20by%20betraying%20Shiva%20cannot%20attain%20me%20even%20in%20his%20dreams)%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20the%20trust%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20towards%20the%20Sanyasis%2C%20Shaivites%20and%20Shaktas%20means%20that%20they%20have%20either%20ceased%20to%20be%20Hindu%20or%20have%20become%20%E2%80%98anti-Ram%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20this%20group%20that%20distributes%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20certificates%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20may%20be%20the%20case%2C%20the%20matter%20has%20reached%20such%20a%20stage%20that%20a%20Shankaracharya%20has%20asked%20%E2%80%93%20if%20the%20temple%20belongs%20to%20the%20Ramanandis%2C%20why%20were%20donations%20taken%20from%20the%20others%20for%20its%20construction%20and%20why%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20Champat%20Rai%20resign%20and%20hand%20over%20the%20temple%20to%20the%20Ramanandis%3F%20What%20is%20the%20haste%2C%20why%20is%20the%20consecration%20being%20carried%20out%20for%20a%20half-built%20temple%20contrary%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20scriptures%3F%20Why%20is%20politics%20being%20done%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20religion%20by%20ignoring%20the%20questions%20arising%20on%20the%20timing%20and%20method%20of%20the%20ceremony%3F%20And%20why%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20religious%20leader%20and%20a%20politician%20being%20erased%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Full%20Text%20%7C%20'Only%20Political%20Hindus%20Are%20Happy'%3A%20Shankaracharya%20on%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%20Consecration%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Ffull-text-only-political-hindus-are-happy-shankaracharya-on-ayodhya-ram-temple-consecration%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%98Only%20Political%20Hindus%20Are%20Happy%E2%80%99%3A%20Shankaracharya%20on%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%20Consecration%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20one%20must%20note%20that%20the%20Shankaracharya%20has%20no%20objection%20to%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20temple%20by%20Ramanandis.%20Rather%2C%20he%20objects%20to%20the%20politics%20being%20played%20by%20the%20trust%20regarding%20it.%20That%20is%20why%20he%20has%20demanded%20that%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Trust%20hand%20over%20the%20temple%20to%20Ramanandis%20and%20resign.%20Obviously%2C%20in%20his%20eyes%20the%20trust%20is%20neither%20as%20inclusive%20as%20the%20Ramanandi%20sect%2C%20nor%20as%20acceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20many%20dignitaries%20defending%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20trust%20are%20saying%20that%20after%20the%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20boycotted%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20it%20was%20necessary%20for%20the%20trust%20to%20declare%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20temple.%20But%20could%20these%20remarks%20not%20have%20been%20made%20in%20a%20different%20way%2C%20which%20would%20have%20made%20it%20look%20a%20little%20more%20civilised%20or%20had%20left%20scope%20for%20brushing%20it%20off%20as%20a%20personal%20opinion%3F%20These%20gentlemen%20have%20no%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20great%20men%20also%20claim%20that%20despite%20the%20long%20and%20strong%20tradition%20of%20reviving%20and%20uniting%20the%20%E2%80%98dispersed%20Sanatan%20Samaj%E2%80%99%20and%20establishing%20a%20new%20philosophy%2C%20Shankaracharya%20is%20not%20the%20Pope%20or%20Caliph%20of%20Hindus.%20But%20when%20asked%20whether%20Champat%20Rai%20is%20the%20Pope%20or%20Caliph%20of%20Hindus%20%E2%80%93%20they%20again%20have%20no%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20not%20the%20only%20problem.%20Even%20though%20Champat%20Rai%20named%20Sanyasis%2C%20Shaivites%20and%20Shaktas%2C%20the%20temple%E2%80%99s%20unannounced%20ownership%20lies%20with%20many%20other%20personalities%20and%20communities.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20belongs%20to%20Sita%2C%20the%20life%20partner%20of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20who%20does%20not%20even%20own%20Ayodhya%20owing%20to%20the%20game%20of%20patriarchy.%20When%20Deepika%20Chikhalia%2C%20who%20played%20the%20role%20of%20Sita%20in%20the%20much-talked%20about%20serial%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20got%20the%20invite%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20she%20expressed%20her%20sadness%20%E2%80%93%20saying%20that%20while%20there%20is%20the%20child%20form%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20the%20temple%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20better%20if%20Mother%20Sita%20had%20been%20given%20a%20place%20beside%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20trust%2C%20along%20with%20Sita%2C%20the%20uninvited%20Ayodhya%20residents%20are%20also%20strangers%2C%20who%20during%20the%20consecration%20of%20%E2%80%98Apne%20Ram%E2%80%99%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20stay%20at%20home%20and%20watch%20the%20ceremony%20on%20TV%20or%20visit%20nearby%20temples%20for%20worship%2C%20and%20celebrate%20with%20fireworks%20like%20Diwali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20there%20is%20also%20no%20plan%20to%20honour%20those%20%3Cem%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20were%20lathicharged%20and%20shot%20in%20the%201990s%20and%20declared%20%E2%80%98martyrs%E2%80%99.%20Votes%20were%20garnered%20by%20showing%20videos%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98martyrdom%E2%80%99%20too.%20He%20believes%20that%20India%20is%20a%20country%20of%20martyrs%20and%20those%20who%20laid%20their%20lives%20were%20martyred%20due%20to%20their%20own%20inspiration.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20soldiers%20are%20sacrificed%2C%20it%20comes%20to%20mind%20after%2010-20%20years%20that%20something%20should%20be%20done%20to%20commemorate%20them.%20A%20pillar%20is%20erected%20in%20their%20memory.%20Some%20names%20are%20mentioned%20but%20what%20was%20built%20for%20whom%20is%20forgotten%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERai%20forgot%20to%20correctly%20add%20the%20years%20while%20making%20this%20remark%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20been%2033%20years%20since%20the%20%E2%80%98martyrdom%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20not%2010%20or%2020%20years.%20People%20have%20different%20opinions%20regarding%20this%20mistake.%20Some%20people%20say%20that%20when%20a%20person%20is%20very%20happy%2C%20he%20messes%20up%20such%20additions%20and%20subtractions%3B%20others%20opine%20that%20such%20mistakes%20happen%20when%20a%20person%20is%20tense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20others%20who%20point%20out%20that%20Champat%20Rai%20and%20his%20troop%20are%20not%20used%20to%20working%20for%20the%20unity%20and%20harmony%20of%20the%20country.%20Now%2C%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20work%20for%20unity%20even%20among%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKrishna%20Pratap%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F265789%2Fayodhya-ram-mandir-champat-rai-ramanandis-shaiv-shakt%2F%5C%22%3EHindi%20original%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705814969000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16152114%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-16-at-9.33.52-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fchampat-rai-ayodhya-ram-temple-shaiva%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Champat%20Rai's%20attitude%20towards%20Sanyasis%2C%20Shaivites%20and%20Shaktas%20goes%20against%20Hindu%20traditions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fchampat-rai-ayodhya-ram-temple-shaiva%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FPIs%20turn%20cautious%2C%20pull%20out%20Rs%2013%2C000%20cr%20from%20Indian%20stocks%20in%20Jan%3A%20Data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705814953000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-11%2F01%2Ffull%2F1667321312-6946.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Ffpis-turn-cautious-pull-out-rs-13-000-cr-from-indian-stocks-in-jan-data-124012100126_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Besides%2C%20FPIs%20were%20big%20sellers%20in%20other%20emerging%20markets%20such%20as%20Taiwan%2C%20South%20Korea%20and%20Hong%20Kong%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus