%22%3ESherlock%20Holmes%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20Vaidyanath%20Sami%20and%20his%20officers%20caught%20the%20culprits%20of%20his%20horrific%20crime%20using%20the%20laundry%20mark%20(tag)%20of%20burnt%20pieces%20of%20clothing%20found%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20this%20horrific%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20they%20solved%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20the%20laundry%20mark%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20Dhaval%20describes%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20%E2%80%9CDeshmukh%20and%20his%20team%20rushed%20to%20the%20scene%20and%20observed%20that%20the%20gas%20pipe%20in%20the%20kitchen%20was%20loose.%20He%20hence%20went%20to%20the%20kitchen%20and%20closed%20the%20gas%20connection.%20He%20found%20four%20bodies%20in%20the%20flat%20with%20multiple%20stab%20wounds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bodies%20had%20been%20covered%20with%20newspapers%20and%20clothes%2C%20and%20it%20appeared%20that%20an%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20set%20fire%20to%20the%20bodies%20and%20the%20flat%20as%20well%20by%20opening%20the%20gas%20pipe.%20The%20bedroom%20was%20ransacked%2C%20and%20cash%20and%20jewels%20were%20missing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20goes%20on%20to%20add.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20were%20Choonawala%2C%20his%20wife%20Roshan%2C%20four-year-old%20grandson%20Shajitkhan%20%5B%20also%20spelled%20Sajid%20Khan%5D%2C%20and%20their%20house%20help%20Annie%20Fernandes.%20All%20four%20of%20the%20victims%20were%20stabbed%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Queen%20of%20Indian%20Pop%3A%20The%20Authorised%20Biography%20of%20Usha%20Uthup%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20written%20by%20Vikram%20Kumar%20Jha%20and%20translated%20by%20Srishti%20Jha%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5BMohammad%20Siddiqui%5D%20Chunawala%20was%20a%20big%20businessman%20and%20his%20murder%20had%20put%20the%20Gamdevi%20Police%20Station%20in%20a%20deep%20shock.%20Curfew%20was%20enforced%20in%20the%20area%20under%20the%20police%20station%E2%80%99s%20jurisdiction.%20Ultimately%2C%20seeing%20no%20developments%20in%20this%20puzzling%20murder%20case%2C%20the%20inspector%20of%20the%20Gamdevi%20Police%20Station%20called%20%5BDCP%5D%20Vaidyanath%20Sami%20and%20communicated%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation.%20He%20requested%20the%20latter%20to%20help%20in%20the%20investigation.%E2%80%9D%20%5B*both%20the%20%E2%80%98Choonawala%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Chunawala%E2%80%98%20spellings%20have%20been%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20businessman%20murdered%20in%20this%20case*%5D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%20request%2C%20DCP%20Vaidyanath%20dispatched%20his%20officers%20to%20the%20scene.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20evidence%3A%3Cbr%3ESoon%2C%20officers%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20CID-Crime%20or%20the%20Crime%20branch%20like%20inspector%20Vinayak%20Vakatkar%2C%20and%20sub-inspectors%20Tatyasaheb%20Goud%20and%20Ramchandra%20Dudhat%20arrived%20at%20the%20scene.%20They%20came%20to%20know%20that%20on%20the%20previous%20day%2C%20Choonawala%20had%20returned%20home%20from%20Radio%20Club%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzQjVJqsQzd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzQjVJqsQzd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dhaval%20Kulkarni%20(%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A3%E0%A5%80)%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40dhavalkulkarni)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdhavalkulkarni%2Fstatus%2F1745164537689747772%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinayak%20Vakatkar%20was%20a%20legendary%20officer%20in%20the%20Bombay%20Police%20crime%20branch.%20His%20cases%20and%20investigations%20made%20it%20to%20the%20newspapers%20and%20the%20works%20of%20local%20crime%20writers.%20Vakatkar%20eventually%20retired%20as%20an%20assistant%20commissioner%20of%20police.%20PSI%20Tatyasaheb%20