r%20cloth%20found%20in%20the%20flat%20had%20the%20AI%20SBH%20laundry%20mark.%20However%2C%20all%20the%20other%20clothes%20found%20in%20the%20house%20had%20the%20J%20MSC%20laundry%20mark%2C%20making%20it%20evident%20that%20the%20shirt%20and%20cloth%20belonged%20to%20the%20assailants.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20fingerprints%20were%20also%20detected%20on%20surfaces%20like%20the%20refrigerator%20in%20the%20dining%20hall.%20A%20blood-stained%20knife%20was%20also%20found.%20However%2C%20the%20fingerprints%20did%20not%20tally%20with%20those%20of%20the%20deceased%20or%20with%20the%20criminals%20in%20the%20records%20of%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECatching%20the%20culprits%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20discovering%20the%20pieces%20of%20clothes%20found%20at%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20Inspector%20Vakatkar%20located%2012%20laundries%20in%20the%20city%20which%20used%20this%20laundry%20mark.%20On%2024%20October%2C%20the%20police%20finally%20zeroed%20in%20on%20the%20American%20Express%20laundry%20at%20Khetwadi%20and%20located%20its%20proprietor%20Shenolikar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20promptly%20told%20the%20PSIs%20Goud%20and%20Dudhat%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98AI%20SBH%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98AI%20Z%E2%80%99%20laundry%20marks%20belonged%20to%20his%20laundry%2C%20and%20the%20two%20male%20customers%20whom%20they%20belonged%20to%20stayed%20in%20the%20same%20locality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20arrests%3A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOn%20the%20same%20evening%2C%20the%20two%20accused%20Sayed%20Bakar%20Hussain%20and%20Sayed%20Ali%20Asad%20were%20arrested%20at%20Khetwadi%20back%20road.%20The%20two%20confessed%20to%20having%20committed%20the%20crime%20for%20pecuniary%20gain.%20They%20had%20stolen%20cash%2C%20gold%20and%20pearl%20ornaments%20and%20wrist%20watches%20worth%20Rs%2010%2C000.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22ht