s%2C%20the%20police%20had%20nabbed%20the%20culprits%20and%20a%20court%20found%20them%20guilty%20and%20sentenced%20them.%20This%20remarkable%20quadruple%20murder%20case%20was%20among%20the%20last%20cases%20of%20DCP%20Vaidyanath%20Sami%E2%80%99s%20illustrious%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20587px)%20100vw%2C%20587px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FFingerprint-PNG-1705587151.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22587%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Murder%20case%20fingerprints%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FFingerprint-PNG-1705587151.jpg%20587w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FFingerprint-PNG-1705587151-226x300.jpg%20226w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FFingerprint-PNG-1705587151-500x664.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FFingerprint-PNG-1705587151-150x199.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338592%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFingerprints%20of%20the%20culprits%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20brief%20note%20on%20DCP%20Vaidyanath%20Sami%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20tenure%20in%20the%20Bombay%20Police%2C%20which%20ran%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades%2C%20DCP%20Vaidyanath%20Someshwar%20Sami%20solved%20many%20mysteries%20in%20ruthless%20criminal%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20however%2C%20he%20had%20never%20imagined%20that%20he%20would%20join%20the%20police%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20on%2021%20November%2C%201908%2C%20in%20the%20then%20Bombay%2C%20Vaidyanath%20came%20from%20a%20rich%20lineage%20but%20humble%20beginnings.%20Although%20he%20was%20a%20descendent%20of%20Sir%20Kumarapuram%20Sheshadri