%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Vaidyanath-Sami-1705586304-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Vaidyanath-Sami-1705586304-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338574%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDCP%20Vaidyanath%20Sami%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20Bombay%20Police%E2%80%99s%20crime%20branch%20for%2028%20years%20and%20retired%20as%20deputy%20commissioner%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20his%20career.%20His%20image%20in%20the%20Bombay%20Police%20was%20that%20of%20an%20impossible%20and%2C%20yet%2C%20intelligent%20officer%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Jha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20an%20investigative%20policeman%20in%20the%20truest%20sense.%20As%20Jha%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20researching%20a%20case%2C%20Sami%20would%20often%20visit%20the%20local%20tea%20shops%20and%20salons%20on%20street%20corners.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20believed%20that%20an%20investigation%20was%20like%20hunting%20with%20deep%20patience.%20One%20has%20to%20keep%20one%E2%80%99s%20sixth%20sense%20in%20a%20complete%20state%20of%20alertness.%20During%20the%20quest%2C%20he%20would%20also%20fully%20utilise%20Bombay%20Police%E2%80%99s%20Fingerprint%20Bureau%20and%20the%20Police%20Dog%20Squad.%20He%20placed%20informers%20in%20almost%20all%20the%20colonies%20in%20the%20then%20Bombay%2C%20He%20would%20only%20rest%20once%20he%20had%20enough%20evidence%20against%20the%20accused%20so%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20away%20in%20the%20court%20for%20the%20lack%20of%20it.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20against%20the%20practice%20of%20third-degree%20torture%20of%20criminals%20as%20he%20found%20it%20quite%20inhuman%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20book%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20career%2C%20he%20solved%20many%20high-prof