leged%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338571%2Fmumbai-portia-putatunda-free-school-planet-spiti-foundation-in-komic-himachal-pradesh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20My%20Grandpa%2C%20a%2090-YO%20Forest%20Officer%20Helped%20Design%20the%20Perfect%20Sustainable%20Jungle%20Retreat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20the%20fondest%20memories%20you%20have%20of%20your%20grandparents%3F%20For%20Luv%20Shekhawat%2C%20it%20is%20childhood%20birthdays%20celebrated%20in%20the%20forests%20of%20Jaipur%20with%20his%20paternal%20grandfather.%20They%20would%20munch%20on%20fruits%20while%20birdsong%20provided%20the%20music%20for%20the%20day.%20%E2%80%9CGood%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Luv%20reminiscing%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20grandfather%20who%20served%20as%20a%20Divisional%20Forest%20Officer%20(DFO)%20certainly%20had%20its%20advantages.%20According%20to%20Luv%2C%20it%20not%20only%20brought%20certain%20perks%20but%20also%20cultivated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332168%2Ftadoba-maharashtra-vacation-sustainable-homestay-by-wildlife-conservation-experts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20growing%20passion%20for%20the%20outdoors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20wildlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%20the%20year%202010%20when%20he%20bought%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20Sariska%20Tiger%20Reserve%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Alwar%2C%20the%20deja%20vu%20was%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20once%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20the%20forest%20is%20where%20I%20always%20belonged.%20It%20was%20in%20my%20destiny%20to%20return.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20the%20rugged%20terrain%20of%20Alwar%20nor%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20the%20proximity%20to%20the%20famous%20(and%20controversi