omplaints%20at%20cybercrime.gov.in%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20unfortunately%2C%20Murthy%20lost%20his%20phone%20while%20travelling%20to%20a%20village.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20me%20two%20days%20to%20retrieve%20all%20my%20old%20data.%20I%20searched%20the%20same%20old%20app%20to%20pay%20the%20loan%20amount.%20But%20as%20it%20was%20an%20unauthorised%20app%2C%20it%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20Play%20Store.%20So%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20pay%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Murthy%20found%20out%20that%20the%20criminal%20had%20circulated%20his%20naked%20morphed%20images%20labelling%20him%20a%20%E2%80%98rapist%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98fraudster%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98kidnapper%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20trauma%20was%20so%20much%20that%20my%20phone%20would%20constantly%20ring%20as%20they%20continued%20to%20share%20my%20photos%20with%20all%20my%20contacts%20from%20different%20numbers.%20I%20was%20getting%20up%20to%201%2C300%20calls%20and%201%2C500%20broadcast%20messages%20in%20an%20hour.%20I%20lost%20my%20concentration%20on%20work.%20And%20I%20had%20already%20lost%20my%20dignity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20my%20hometown%2C%20my%20parents%20were%20mentally%20tortured%20by%20relatives%20and%20society.%20They%20are%20teachers%20by%20profession%2C%20so%20they%20were%20questioned%20for%20their%20teachings%20for%20other%20kids%20at%20school%20when%20their%20own%20son%20was%20%E2%80%98unethical%E2%80%99.%20I%20wanted%20to%20explain%20to%20everyone%20I%20was%20innocent%2C%20but%20my%20own%20parents%20did%20not%20believe%20me.%20I%20was%20getting%20depressed%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20one%20day%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20then-commissioner%20of%20police%20V%20C%20Sajjanar.%20A%20conversatio