0change%20the%20phone%20number.%20In%20cases%20of%20harassment%20and%20defamation%2C%20I%20also%20help%20the%20victims%20find%20the%20locations%20of%20the%20criminals%20using%20IP%20addresses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurthy%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20has%20not%20only%20helped%20other%20victims%20but%20also%20helped%20him%20regain%20his%20identity%20and%20affection%20from%20his%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20only%20after%20a%20year%20when%20my%20father%20finally%20understood%20me.%20He%20literally%20took%20me%20into%20his%20arms%20and%20broke%20down%20for%20having%20misunderstood%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Murthy%20worked%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20cyber%20security%20volunteering%20force%20for%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338446%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMurthy%20worked%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20cyber%20security%20volunteering%20force%20for%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFive%20important%20steps%20for%20cybercrime%20victims%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20his%20own%20experience%2C%20Murthy%20offers%20five%20simple%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F81790%2Fdhanya-menon-cybercrime-investigation-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafeguard%20individuals%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20cybercrime%20and%20outlines%20essential%20steps%20that%20victims%20of%20cybercrime%20should%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Secure%20your%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20it%20is%20very%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20your%20data%20is%20secured.%20When%20you%20access%20any%20application%2C%20you%20do%20not%20just%20install%20the%20app%2C%20you%20give%20it%20access%20to%20your%20camera%2C%20contacts%2C%20Gmail%20account%2C%20and%20location.%20I%20suggest%20you%20install%20only%20very%20crucial%20apps%20and%20avoid%20giving%20them%20unnecessary%20access.%20Also%2C%20we%20must%20regularly%20check%20if%20our%20apps%20have%20any%20kind%20of%20access%20they%20should%20actually%20not%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMinimise%20the%20use%20of%20Gmail%20everywhere%20because%20if%20your%20phone%20is%20hacked%2C%20the%20hacker%20gets%20access%20to%20your%20phone%20and%20contacts%20because%20Gmail%20is%20linked%20to%20your%20contacts%20and%20gallery.%20Also%2C%20you%20must%20mask%20the%20camera%20on%20your%20laptop%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Change%20your%20privacy%20settings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20of%20cybercrime%2C%20firstly%20your%20WhatsApp%20is%20compromised.%20So%2C%20I%20suggest%20you%20ensure%20end-to-end%20encryption%20on%20WhatsApp.%20Also%2C%20many%20people%20do%20not%20know%20that%20they%20can%20choose%20%E2%80%98silence%20unknown%20callers%E2%80%99%20and%20protect%20their%20IP%20addresses%20by%20changing%20privacy%20settings.%20You%20must%20enable%20it%20to%20secure%20yourself%20from%20cybercriminals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Reboot%20your%20phone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179257%2Fmumbai-couple-troll-police-cyberbullying-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evictim%20of%20cybercrime%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20you%20should%20first%20deactivate%20your%20WhatsApp%20account%20immediately%20and%20remove%20photos%20from%20the%20gallery.%20Thereafter%2C%20you%20must%20reboot%20your%20phone.%20This%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20hacker%20loses%20access%20to%20your%20data%20and%20all%20the%20apps%20are%20closed%20automatically%2C%E2%80%9D%20suggests%20Murthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20police%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20our%20work%2C%20we%20can%20trace%20the%20location%20but%20not%20the%20person.%20It%20is%20illegal.%20It%20is%20the%20police%20whom%20one%20should%20seek%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20of%20harassment%20or%20defamation%20on%20social%20media%20verticals%20like%20Instagram%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20Facebook%2C%20police%20write%20to%20their%20parent%20company%20Meta%20and%20report%20the%20profile.%20They%20will%20monitor%20their%20cookies%2C%20browsing%20history%2C%20and%20messages.%20So%2C%20not%20only%20will%20they%20find%20their%20location%20using%20the%20IP%20address%20but%20also%20identify%20the%20criminal.%20So%2C%20the%20right%20way%20is%20to%20approach%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Register%20your%20complaint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurthy%20advises%20victims%20to%20report%20cyber%20complaints%20at%